  "instructions": [
    "Chop the vegetables into small pieces.",
    "In a wok or large skillet, sauté onions until translucent.",
    "Add minced garlic and cook for another minute.",
    "Fold in beef and stir-fry until seared on all sides.",
    "Pour in tomato paste and mix well to create a thick sauce base.",
    "Add water or broth. Bring the mixture to a simmer, then reduce heat to low.",
    "Cover and let it simmer for about 20 minutes.",
    "Stir in mixed herbs and adjust seasoning with salt and pepper.",
    "Turn off the heat once the beef is fully cooked and juices are released.",
    "Serve hot over rice or noodles."
